4
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:52,170
If what was said in the livestream is true,

5
00:00:52,920 --> 00:00:56,250
then I'm afraid there's a traitor within our research team.

6
00:00:57,280 --> 00:00:59,120
I won't allow anyone

7
00:00:59,760 --> 00:01:02,690
to destroy the results you protected with your life.

8
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:04,700
No matter who it is,

9
00:01:05,640 --> 00:01:07,800
I will definitely find this traitor.

10
00:01:12,080 --> 00:01:12,960
This time,

11
