24
00:03:12,200 --> 00:03:12,840
Forget it.

25
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:14,000
This is too important.

26
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:15,660
I'll just go see her directly.

27
00:03:19,760 --> 00:03:20,200
No.

28
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:23,560
Excuse me, officers.

29
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,200
No.

30
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,800
You've got the wrong person.

31
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:28,640
No.

32
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:44,240
Officer Cao, it's you.

33
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:44,720
