52
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:04,280
I need to contact Director Yang.

53
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:05,680
You don't need to call me.

54
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:12,480
All of this

55
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:14,480
was done on my orders.

56
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:16,900
Director Yang,

57
00:05:17,400 --> 00:05:18,480
