58
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:20,640
This involves national interests,

59
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:22,240
I must be cautious.

60
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,340
Director Yang,

61
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:27,240
without my theoretical work,

62
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:29,520
this experiment would never have been possible.

63
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:32,250
I made controlled nuclear fusion a possibility.

64
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:34,159
If I wanted to leak information,

65
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:37,420
I wouldn't have collaborated with you from the beginning.

66
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:39,280
That point

67
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:40,820
has occurred to me too.

68
00:05:41,320 --> 00:05:42,800
But faced with the evidence,

69
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:45,280
I've considered another possibility.

70
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:47,720
What if from the beginning

71
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:49,640
you had planned to work with foreign entities,

72
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:50,480
but because

73
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,720
Professor Wu discovered this

74
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:52,320
and consequently

75
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:54,650
you were forced to join the research team?

76
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:57,840
That would also make sense.

77
00:05:59,280 --> 00:06:00,440
Director Yang,

78
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:03,040
you've seen everything I've done.

79
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:05,000
I couldn't possibly do such a thing.

80
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:07,320
How could you suspect me?

81
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:10,080
Dongfeng,

82
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:13,090
