83
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:15,040
but the evidence points to you.

84
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,880
Only when

85
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:20,120
the investigation is complete

86
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:22,240
