89
00:06:30,880 --> 00:06:31,760
Treat him

90
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:33,600
well.

91
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:36,600
Until the final results come out,

92
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:39,600
Lin Dongfeng is still our comrade.

93
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,920
Why did you arrest Lin Dongfeng?

94
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,240
It's classified information,

95
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,770
I can't disclose anything.

96
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:07,840
Don't think I don't know

97
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:10,800
that you've had Cao Dahua investigating us.

98
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:12,660
