99
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:14,360
Dongfeng has dedicated himself to this project.

100
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,840
He's worked so hard.

101
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:18,100
How could he possibly leak information?

102
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,400
Could you?

103
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:22,280
