104
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:23,720
We need evidence.

105
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,320
Stop causing trouble here.

106
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:26,960
Go home.

107
00:07:27,960 --> 00:07:29,040
Search your conscience.

108
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,760
If Lin Dongfeng leaked information,

109
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:33,960
