110
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:36,960
There are things you don't understand.

111
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:39,090
And I don't need to explain them to you.

112
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:43,380
Yang Zhengdao.

113
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:46,159
You're abusing your power.

114
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,960
If there's an internal investigation,

115
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:50,560
