129
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:27,240
Anyway,

130
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:30,160
until the investigation is over,

131
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:30,890
Lin Dongfeng

132
00:08:31,200 --> 00:08:32,919
