144
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:31,730
Don't worry.

145
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:34,040
I'll definitely prove your innocence.

146
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:35,400
Actually,

147
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:37,260
I already have some ideas.

148
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:40,240
I've carefully examined all the research team members

149
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:42,680
and found none of them had any motive to leak information.

150
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:43,800
So it's highly likely

151
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:45,080
that it was someone on the periphery of the research team,

152
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:47,210
staff who had access to the materials.

153
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:48,320
Indeed,

154
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:50,740
all the academicians are very reliable.

155
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:51,280
Also,

156
00:09:52,160 --> 00:09:53,820
among the evidence against me

157
00:09:54,040 --> 00:09:56,570
is a contract signed by Gu Bingqing and Smith.

158
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:59,000
But I've thought carefully about it.

159
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,680
At the time the contract was signed,

160
00:10:00,680 --> 00:10:02,520
I was with Gu Bingqing.

161
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:05,040
So this contract must be forged.

162
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:08,080
Since both Gu Bingqing and I are being framed,

163
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:10,560
