167
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:20,640
Wait for me.

168
00:10:20,640 --> 00:10:22,640
I'll definitely get you out of here.

169
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,040
Who are you?

170
00:10:39,040 --> 00:10:40,000
