186
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:06,120
Miss Gu Bingqing of Huasheng Group.

187
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,320
So you mean

188
00:11:09,760 --> 00:11:11,090
all those things before

189
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:12,880
